     "img:audit": "Optimize every shipped/inlined SVG under web/ in place with SVGO (visually-lossless preset; keeps viewBox). Idempotent — re-running only rewrites new/edited SVGs. Skips generator-input SVGs (large-image.svg, styles/source.svg)",
     "img:audit:check": "CI guard for img:audit: fail if any SVG under web/ isn't already optimized (drift detector; run img:audit and commit to fix)",
